HB 448 Original 2026 Regular Session Adams
Abstract: Authorizes the use of certain scholarships for former firefighters and spouses of
former firefighters for a master's degree.
Present law provides for scholarships for the following categories of people:
(1) A firefighter who is injured in his line of duty in which injury results in the inability
to remain employed.
